content.original: Clan Grade Artemis Munitions have a more capable guidance system, allowing for a far tighter spread. Upon receiving a Critical Hit, any remaining ammunition stored inside an Ammo Bin will explode dealing damage to the install location. Risk can be mitigated with the use of C.A.S.E.
